Ḥemleɣ tacennayt Joan Baez.
Ḥemleɣ acennay Ɛli Ɛemren.
Tizlatin-is srunt-iyi acḥal n tikal.
D asenfaṛ yelhan.
Taqbaylit teḥwaǧ aṭas n isura i warrac.
Nurar tiqqar ass mi nella meẓẓiyit.
Ḥemleɣ ad waliɣ udem-iw deg wallen-im.
Nniɣ-am, ḥemleɣ-kem a ddin uqabac!
Tefkiḍ-iyi axessaṛ.
Debdebeɣ fell-am.
Taxdeɣ fell-am
Ttewteɣ fell-am.
Cewḍeɣ fell-am.
Selbeɣ fell-am.
Ččiɣ iḥeckulen fell-am.
Ǧǧiɣ imawlan-iw fell-am.
Nuɣeɣ akked gma fell-am.
D kem kan, ma mači d kem a wer zwaǧ.
Dubeɣ fell-am.
Nettat tettwaxḍeb ma d nek nejlaɣ.
Texdeɛḍ-iyi ad kem-yexdeɛ rebbi!
Texdeɛḍ-iyi ad k-yexdeɛ rebbi!
Swiɣ snat n tqaɛunin n crab mebla učči fell-am.
Uriɣ isem-im s lmus ɣef yiɣil-iw.
Urgaɣ tegneḍ yid-i.
Urgaɣ uɣeɣ-kem.
Urgaɣ sɛiɣ dderya yid-m.
Yeggul baba-m fell-i.

